# Changelog

## [Unreleased]

## [0.18.1] - 2025-11-05

### Changed
- packaging: migrated metadata to pyproject.toml

### Fixed
- ui/scheduler: error in cronrule explanation

## [0.18.0] - 2025-08-29

### Changed
- replaced sqlalchemy with sqlhelp throughout
- schema: follow changes in sqlhelp
- tests: postgresql db handling moved to sqlhelp
- decoder: more intolerant spec decoder
- elm: repaired tests

### Fixed
- blueprint: missing .to_dict call on a row

## [0.17.0] - 2025-02-27

### Added
- monitor: show vacuum policy

### Fixed
- blueprint: cron rule validation
- cli: follow simplification in rework

## [0.16.0] - 2024-10-25

### Changed
- ci: moved to heptapod
- blueprint: webapp instanciable without tsview
- blueprint: show ui even when nothing registered
- headers: title changes and removed unnecessary CDNs

### Fixed
- scheduling: typing bug for web schedule definition
- blueprint: cron rule validation tests

## [0.15.1] - 2024-08-23

### Fixed
- makefile: optimized js output

## [0.15.0] - 2024-03-07

### Added
- menu: stand alone menu for main view, logs, errors and info
- plan: tab showing next hour schedule plan with configurable hours
- inputs/bool: improved true state handling

### Changed
- templates: removed unused cruft
- elm: added style to page title
- model: canwrite attribute for permission control
- elm: forbid mutating actions when canwrite is false

### Fixed
- getiofilehint: transformed to POST
- plan: refresh plan list at hours change

## [0.14.0] - 2023-11-20

### Added
- ui: decode default field for launchers
- plan tab for schedule visualization
- permission controls with canwrite attribute

### Changed
- replaced apscheduler with croniter (python-icron)
- templates: avoid browser quirks mode
- build: basic CI system with linter checks
- main/init: use record for readability

### Fixed
- inputs/bool: handling of true state
- lazy loading repairs
- used new unprepare rework api call

## [0.13.0] - 2023-10-17

### Added
- launcher: boolean input support
- __version__ attribute in package root

### Changed
- tasks: lazy loading with batch loads
- tasks: filters on service name and inputs
- initial tasks table load by batches to avoid long loading times

### Fixed
- blueprint/formatinput: stop cutting long content

## [0.12.0] - 2023-09-29

### Added
- scheduler: button to immediately launch prepared tasks
- complete action to launch prepared task

### Changed
- style: improved scheduler buttons

### Fixed
- blueprint/iofilehint: crash when no task list

## [0.11.0] - 2022-10-11

### Changed
- blueprint/schedule2: use type converter for well-typed inputs

### Fixed
- pkg: lxml needed for tests

## [0.10.1] - 2022-05-23

### Fixed
- pkg: missing pygments dependency

## [0.10.0] - 2022-04-11

### Added
- info: new view providing complete task information
  - basic info display
  - input and output specs exposure
  - download links for task io blocks
  - links from tasks list to task info page
- tasks: singleton input/output file display
- elm: build files at pip install time

### Changed
- view/defaultrule: non "*" default value
- types: InputSpec renamed to IOSpec
- job_results: better mime type
- tasks: collapsed queued/started/finished columns into one

### Fixed
- followed internal changes in rework

## [0.9.0] - 2021-06-14

### Added
- complete Elm rewrite of UI
  - task table with server-side json endpoints
  - services and workers tables
  - domain filtering and management
  - refresh every 2s with timer management
  - action pending management
  - event table for task cud events
- launcher: tab for web-launchable operations
  - full input spec form generation
  - datetime and moment field support
  - required fields visual cues
  - form open/close/cancel functionality
- scheduler: comprehensive UI for task scheduling
  - schedulers table with creation/deletion
  - form with service/domain selection
  - crontab-like rules with inline documentation
  - rule validation with step-by-step feedback
  - prepared task input display
- logging: simple logging facility
  - log levels filtering
  - identical log lines folding
- log view: replacement task log view with lazy loading
- domains: "all" filter for multi-domain setups

### Changed
- replaced javascript with full Elm implementation
- bootstrap upgraded to 4.5
- ui: numerous refactorings and simplifications
- tasks: order by id
- ui: more precise naming throughout

### Fixed
- cli/view: use find_uri to exploit rework.cfg
- schedule-task: handle no-input file case
- ui: proper domain handling
- ui: user handling fixes
- adjust for werkzeug 1 release

## [0.8.0] - 2020-07-03

### Added
- app: accept prefix parameter
- permission predicate

### Changed
- tasks/table: fetch data in parallel using thread pool

### Fixed
- pkg: README available for pypi

## [0.7.0] - 2020-05-26

### Added
- basic web ui for rework
- tasks, workers, services tables
- domain filtering
- kill action for workers
- tabs for easier layout
- ability to schedule jobs
- show debug ports for services

### Changed
- web: tabs-based layout

### Fixed
- initial release features

## [0.6.0] - 2020-04-08

### Added
